For future reference to anyone looking at this post, you can find the status of the Bluemix platform and its services at this URL: http://ibm.biz/bluemixstatus
Are you attempting this from the Dallas or London/UK region? We are currently experiencing issues with London IoT service.
It was UK. I've tried US and it works.
There was on outage on March 10 in UK region. Full service has been restored, if you are still experiencing the problem today, let us know.
